ocd: Your OCD preference. This can either be sorting `alphabetical` or based on the `length` of the items
registry: The default npm registry we should use for looking up package information
github-clone: The git URL template for when you clone GitHub repositories
token: Personal GitHub access/authorization token which is used to communicate with the API
cols: Maximum length of the console output
algorithm: The cypher algorithm that is used en/decode passwords in your config
